Afrijet Airlines bụ ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu nke nwere isi ụlọ ọrụ ya na NAHCO Building na ala nke Murtala Muhammed International Airport na Ikeja, Nigeria. E guzobere ya nakwa ọ malitere ọrụ ibu na mpaghara n'afọ 1999
Isi ụlọ ọrụ ya bụ Murtala Mohammed International Airport.
Tinyere ịrụ ọrụ ibu site na Naijiria, ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọelu ahụ na-arụkwa ọrụ ụgbọ elu nchebe dị elu na Democratic Republic of Congo
Ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọelu ahụ esila n'ọfịs ya na Murtala Mohammed International Airport kwaga n'isi ụlọ ọrụ ya na Opebi, Lagos
Ọ ka na-elekọta ụlọ ahịa mmezi ụgbọ elu na ụlọ ọrụ Elite Aviation.
Gọọmentị Naịjirịa setịpụrụ oge a kara aka n'April 30, 2007 maka ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọ elu niile na-arụ ọrụ na mba ahụ iji mee ndozighari ma ọ bụ ha akwusi ọrụ, na mgbalị iji hụ na ọrụ na nchekwa ka mma
Ụlọ ọrụ ụgbọelu ahụ mezuru ụkpụrụ nke Nigerian Civil Aviation Authority n'ihe gbasara ndozighari ụlọọrụ ma debanye aha ya maka ọrụ
Otú ọ dị, na 2009, e mechiri Afrijet Airlines.
